Title: {FETCH_STORY_DETAILS.title}
URL: {FETCH_STORY_DETAILS.url}
Score: {FETCH_STORY_DETAILS.score} ({FETCH_STORY_DETAILS.descendants} comments)

Top comments:
{FETCH_STORY_DETAILS.comments}

Write exactly two sentences:
1. What the story is about — name the actual subject, technology, person, or claim. No "this article discusses" framing.
2. The most interesting take from the comments — paraphrase a specific opinion or counterpoint, not "people are debating it."

Be direct. No hedging.
